# Documentation Location

All markdown documentation files (`.md`) should be placed in the `.\docs` folder.

## Rules

- Create new documentation files in `docs/` at the project root
- Do NOT create `.md` files in other directories unless they are README files
- README.md files are allowed at project root and in subdirectories

## Examples

```
# ✅ GOOD
docs/DB2-Utility-Monitoring-Guide.md
docs/Alert-Configuration-Guide.md
README.md

# ❌ BAD
ServerMonitorAgent/DB2-Guide.md
notes/documentation.md
```
